    • Consumer

      public Consumer​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String email, java.lang.String phoneNumber, java.lang.String address, java.lang.String password)
      Create a new Consumer with an empty list of bookings and default Covid-19 preferences
      Parameters:
      name - full name of the Consumer
      email - email address of the Consumer (used to log in to the application and for event cancellation notifications)
      phoneNumber - phone number of the Consumer (used for event cancellation notifications)
      address - address of the Consumer (optional)
      password - password used to log in to the application
